item.description:
@gravenfire234 wrote:

[quote=“Stupit, post:14, topic:410622”][quote author=gravenfire234 link=topic=511900.msg3715021#msg3715021 date=1313584281]

they will only sue you if you don’t state it’s for educational purposes and/or making money from it and not giving some to them

If i am making money out of a server how am i suppose to give them?
[/quote]http://www.moparisthebest.com/lawstuff You dont need to go them anything emulation is legal and they cant shut down you site if you dont host anything on it I.E a webclient or your cache which could be avoided by making your server compatible with the moparscape client.

l2read. also, gl with getting banned for ban evading.[/quote]I am not evading nor am i banned my account gravenfire23 had its password reset due to the moparcraft server bug, me being an idiot lost the password to my email account i used to register making it impossible to recover the account. So then i had no choice but to create another account to PM MITB about the situation but i have yet to get a response l2notasumethings kthxbai
